sequenceDiagram
    actor System_Timer as System (Timer)
    participant System
    actor Player
    
    Note over System_Timer, Player: UC-10: Enemy AI Turn (Spawn & Move)
    System_Timer->>System: triggerSpawnEvent()
    System->>System: countActiveEnemies()
    
    alt Active enemies < 5
        System->>System: getRandomEdgeTile()
        System->>System: instantiateEnemy(randomType)
        System-->>Player: renderNewEnemyAt(x,y)
    end
    
    loop For each Knight within 5 tiles
        System->>System: calculatePathfinding(Hero)
        System->>System: updateKnightPosition()
        System-->>Player: renderEnemyMove()
    end